casebody.data:
MICHIGAMME OIL CO. et al. v. CONTINENTAL OIL CO. Circuit Court of Appeals, Sixth Circuit. June 8, 1938. Miller, Bevan, Horwitz & DesRoches, of Detroit, Mich., and John W. Conlin, of Ann Arbor, Mich., for appellants. Roscoe O. Bonisteel, of Ann Arbor, Mich., for' appellee. •

Before TUCKS, SIMONS, and ALLEN, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Appeal dismissed on stipulation.
